                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290115-125-off649 t18290115-125-crimeloc652"></join>. The prisoner was in my employ, and lodged in the house; these boots are mine - they were taken from a particular shelf in my shop; they are not his own work - he never made any of this sort; they had not been soled - he has been with me about three months.</p>
